  "texts": [
    "We see that in some instances, the model struggles to follow instructions and often deviates from what the task asks for.",
    "Furthermore, models that have undergone reinforcement learning with AI feedback (RLAIF), like FinTral-DPO, ChatGPT, and GPT-4, show even more marked improvements.",
    "Adding RLAIF dramatically boosts performance to the average score of 0.59, resulting in FinTral-DPO outperforming ChatGPT.",
    "GPT-4, in particular, stands out with the highest average score, indicating its robust performance across a diverse set of tasks.",
    "Its high NER, NU, and FD scores suggest exceptional capabilities in understanding complex text, identifying specific entities, and interpreting numerical data."
